headline: NextEra Energy announces settlement rate for corporate units issued in September 2022
summary: NextEra Energy, Inc. (NYSE: NEE) today announced the settlement rate for the stock purchase contracts that are components of corporate units (NYSE: NEE PRR) issued in September 2022. Holders of the corporate units will receive 0.5705 shares of NextEra Energy common stock for each stock purchase contract they hold, with cash to be paid in lieu of any fractional shares. The settlement rate is based upon the average of the closing price per share of NextEra Energy common stock on the New York Stock
